          "Squaring both sides preserves inequality: x² > y²",
          "For square root: √x > √y (not reversed)",
          "For reciprocals: inequality reverses → 1/x < 1/y",
          "x − y > 0"
        ],
        "why_correct": {
          "A": "Squaring positive numbers preserves inequality."
        },
        "why_incorrect": {
